    Trends

    With the resource /trends you can find out which are the 50 products most sought after by users in Mercado Libre. The trends are updated every day in each country (Brasil, Chile, México and Colombia) and you can also see them as follows.


    Search for trends by country

    To know each country's trends, just make a GET to the resource entering SITE ID before parameters. For Mexico: MLM, Brazil: MLB, Chile: MLC and Colombia: MCO.

    Request:

    curl -X GET -H 'Authorization: Bearer $ACCESS_TOKEN'  https://api.mercadolibre.com/trends/$SITE_ID

    Example:

    curl -X GET -H 'Authorization: Bearer $ACCESS_TOKEN'  https://api.mercadolibre.com/trends/MLM

    Trends by country and category

    Request:

    curl -X GET -H 'Authorization: Bearer $ACCESS_TOKEN'  https://api.mercadolibre.com/trends/$SITE_ID/$CATEGORY_ID

    Example:

    curl -X GET -H 'Authorization: Bearer $ACCESS_TOKEN'  https://api.mercadolibre.com/trends/MLM/MLM1575
